    "body": "It's a Qt [bug](https://bugreports.qt.io/browse/QTBUG-88600), i see just a two ways to fix it:\r\n- Upgrade Qt version\r\n- Manually patch Qt cocoa [plugin](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/67597482/qt-qsystemtrayicon-on-mac-is-squashed-in-the-second-screen)\r\n\r\nI did not find any workaround for this issue, here is some discussions from others open-source Qt-users:\r\nhttps://github.com/keepassxreboot/keepassxc/issues/5762\r\nhttps://github.com/nextcloud/desktop/issues/2584",
